  <h2>My Role</h2>
  <p>
    Co-designed with Sam Wolpert. The Meth-An Company team also included Thomas Glenn, Martin Goes,
    and Victoria Filio. I contributed to the thermal cascade architecture, cost analysis modeling,
    and pitch delivery to Ball Corporation judges.
  </p>

